description:
**Benefits:**  

* 401(k)
* 401(k) matching
* Bonus based on performance
* Dental insurance
* Health insurance
* Paid time off
* Vision insurance



Primary responsibilities included:  

* Managing help desk tickets related to user issues for assigned system(s) and provide interdepartmental support by responding to inquiries, troubleshooting problems, and determining solutions;
* Assigned systems include ICE’s Encompass, Microsoft, LON, IDS, and others as necessary;
* Assist users with Encompass login issues, passwords, creating new accounts, loan level assistance, and other tier 1 issues;
* Review LOS system release notes and manage release updates;
* Assist in administering assigned system(s) and oversee processes related to user access, system settings, roles and security, and licensing requirements;
* Guide and assist employees remotely through system configuration, troubleshooting, and maintenance;
* Respond to tech inquiries via email, through Teams chats, or over the phone; and
* Tech inquires may include issues with computer, creating an email account or email group, Adobe issues, Microsoft related issues, etc.





This is a remote position.
